Step 1: Cleanse and exfoliate skin. Step 2: Smooth towelette all over body, unfolding as needed. Step 3: Use sparingly around ankles, knees, and elbows. Step 4: Wash hands thoroughly after use. Step 5: Use daily until you have achieved the desired level of tan, and then apply 1-2 times a week. Best if used within 6 months of purchase.

This product does not contain a sunscreen and does not protect against sunburn. This product contains alpha hydroxyl acid (aha) that may increase your skin's sensitivity to the sun and particularly the possibility of sunburn. Repeated exposure of unprotected skin while tanning may increase the risk of skin aging, skin cancer and other harmful effects to the skin even if you do not burn.
